I forgot you have poor eyesight.

00:43:16.098 --> 00:43:17.933
It’s just the text is small.

00:43:20.402 --> 00:43:22.204
Wait, this one is amazing!

00:43:31.714 --> 00:43:32.548
Huh?

00:43:33.382 --> 00:43:36.118
You’ll die one day too, right, Hatano?

00:43:38.320 --> 00:43:40.556
I love you, Hatano.

00:43:44.093 --> 00:43:45.227
You finally said it.

